---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Disclosure | Logo Brief Guide"
  description="Read the Logo Brief Guide disclosure regarding affiliate relationships and recommendations."
  pathname="/disclosure/"
>
  <section class="prose">
    <p class="eyebrow">Disclosure</p>
    <h1>Disclosure</h1>

    <p>
      Logo Brief Guide may include affiliate links, referral links, or partner
      links on some pages.
    </p>

    <p>
      That means if you click certain links and take an action, this site may
      earn a commission or referral fee at no extra cost to you.
    </p>

    <h2>How this affects recommendations</h2>
    <p>
      The goal of this site is to help people make better buying decisions, not
      to push the most aggressive promotion possible. Any recommendations should
      be based on usefulness, fit, and practical decision-making.
    </p>

    <p>
      Even when a link may generate compensation, you should still evaluate the
      service or provider for your own needs, budget, and standards.
    </p>

    <h2>No guarantees</h2>
    <p>
      Results vary. A tool, freelancer, or agency that works well for one buyer
      may not be the best fit for another.
    </p>

    <h2>Your responsibility</h2>
    <p>
      You are responsible for reviewing the current pricing, policies, terms,
      and deliverables of any third-party service before purchasing.
    </p>

    <p>
      If you have questions about a recommendation on this site, please use the
      <a href="/contact/">Contact</a> page.
    </p>
  </section>
</MainLayout>